data.description: Welcome home to this darling rambler, an alluring home boasting an open concept design situated on a substantial .31 acre lot. In the kitchen, you’ll find white cabinets, a butcher block countertop, and a convenient stovetop island, perfect for creating culinary masterpieces and entertaining. Gas line was just added to the property as well as a new gas stove, heat pump and water heater. Beyond the interior, the charm extends outdoors where you’ll find a spacious back deck, perfect for relaxation, and entertainment.  There is plenty of room for playing, gardening, and enjoying outdoor activities. The property boasts both a detached shop/garage and an attached one-car garage. Take advantage of this short sale and make this home yours today!
